# maintainScore()

## Features
- It updates the score of both the players
- It keeps record of the time

### Scenario: Record the score

  Given: The setup is done and game is going on
  
  When: The right/left paddle moves
  
  Then: Increase the score by on according to which paddle moves
  
### Scenario: Display the winner
  
  Given: The game is going on
    
  When: The timer reaches the set time
    
  Then: Display the winner according to the highest score in the system
  
### Scenario: Paddle miss the ball

  Given: The game is going on
  
  When: The paddle miss the ball
  
  Then: Start the game with the ball on the opposite player side until timer is on and maintain the score also
    
    
